data.name: Cookie explanation
data.value: Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device when you visit our website. They help us provide you with a better experience and understand how you use our service.

data.name: Essential cookies explanation
data.value: These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly and cannot be disabled.

data.name: Authentication cookie description
data.value: Maintains your login session and authentication state

data.name: Security cookie description
data.value: Protects against cross-site request forgery attacks

data.name: Functional cookies explanation
data.value: These cookies enhance your experience by remembering your preferences and settings.

data.name: Display cookie description
data.value: Stores your display preferences and UI settings

data.name: Analytics cookies explanation
data.value: These cookies help us understand how visitors use our website and improve our services.

data.name: Google Analytics cookie description
data.value: Used to distinguish unique users and track website usage

data.name: Session cookie description
data.value: Used to distinguish users and track session data

data.name: Cookie management explanation
data.value: You can control and manage cookies through your browser settings. However, disabling certain cookies may affect the functionality of our website.

data.name: Browser settings notice
data.value: Most browsers allow you to view, manage, and delete cookies. Please refer to your browser's help documentation for specific instructions.

data.name: Third-party cookies explanation
data.value: We may use third-party services that set their own cookies. These services help us provide analytics and improve our website functionality.

data.name: Additional information text
data.value: If you have any questions about our use of cookies or this Cookie Policy, please contact us.

data.name: Essential cookies required
data.value: These cookies are required for the website to function
